r feedback and build delivery, and discuss how to integrate these tools into your development workflow to improve efficiency and streamline your processes.","type":"text"}]},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC23-10108-Whats-new-in-Background-Assets":{"role":"sampleCode","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC23-10108-Whats-new-in-Background-Assets","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc23-10108-whats-new-in-background-assets","title":"What’s new in Background Assets","kind":"article","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Waiting is no fun! Discover how Background Assets can help your app download content before it even launches. We’ll show you how to integrate Background Assets into an existing app, explore when to use essential or non-essential assets, and learn how to make debugging your extension a breeze.","type":"text"}]},"WWDC25-Icon.png":{"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC25-Icon.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-Icon.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"type":"link","title":"Learn More…","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn More…"}],"url":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"},"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2025/325":{"type":"download","checksum":null,"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2025\/325","url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2025\/325"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"type":"image","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png"}]},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC25-328-Whats-new-in-App-Store-Connect":{"role":"sampleCode","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-328-Whats-new-in-App-Store-Connect","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc25-328-whats-new-in-app-store-connect","title":"What’s new in App Store Connect","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Get the latest updates for App Store Connect, including the new web UI for build delivery and enhancements to TestFlight notifications. We’ll also discuss new app discovery features and enhancements, such as keywords for custom product pages, Accessibility Nutrition Labels, and age ratings updates. Additionally, learn about new functionalities like In-App Purchase offer codes and review summarization tools."}],"type":"topic","kind":"article"},"WWDC25.jpg":{"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25.jpg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC25.jpg"}}}